'''polyphosphate'''
#{{chemistry}} any of a [[class]] of [[inorganic polymer]]s containing [[linked]] [[phosphate]] groups; the low [[molecular weight]] [[polymer]]s, such as [[sodium tripolyphosphate]], are used in [[water softening]] and as [[food additive]]s
